# Rasm Core

Rasm targets RhinoWIP on macOS, `.NET 10`, C# 14, GH2, and Eto host assemblies from `/Applications/RhinoWIP.app`.

## Required reads (in order)

1. `CLAUDE.md` — manifest, dependency policy, universal constraints, quality gates
2. Root `AGENTS.md` — navigation, documentation policy, bridge pointer
3. Nearest nested `AGENTS.md` for the folder under edit

## Skills

Use repo `.claude/skills/` only for procedures. Do not create Cursor skills. Fall back to `~/.codex/skills/` only when repo skills do not cover a file type.

## Quality

See `CLAUDE.md` §5.2 for validation rails: `quality static check`, `quality test run`, `quality bridge verify`.

## Rule edits

After changing `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`, verify activation: Cmd+Shift+P → **Show Active Rules**.
